<i>That's Joe's mom,</i>
<i>and Joe is my best friend.</i>

03:20.867 --> 03:23.369
<i>And he's been with me</i>
<i>for 27 years.</i>

03:23.436 --> 03:24.837
Like, he's been on all the peaks

03:24.904 --> 03:26.706
and valleys right next to me,
you know?

03:26.773 --> 03:29.509
-Your right or die. Yeah.
-That's literally it, man.

03:29.576 --> 03:32.845
<i>In Pittsburgh, we have this</i>
<i>thing where the encouragement</i>

03:32.912 --> 03:34.814
