gonna do that. Prove it."

03:39.986 --> 03:42.989
<i>So the thing about Marianne was</i>
<i>when Joe and I were</i>

03:43.056 --> 03:46.559
<i>planning to go to California</i>
<i>and chase this dream, you know,</i>

