and, you know, we start

04:21.027 --> 04:23.496
laughing,
and it's just family and...

04:23.563 --> 04:26.866
and I wanted
to not only thank her,

04:26.933 --> 04:30.903
but I wanted to do this
as respect to my best friend

04:30.970 --> 04:33.873
