39:51.188 --> 39:53.758
-So pretty.
-And-and Rob got all the floors

39:53.824 --> 39:55.126
<i>uh, refinished</i>
<i>so that they've...</i>

39:55.192 --> 39:56.627
<i>they've got life in 'em again.</i>

39:56.694 --> 39:58.596
<i>MARIANNE:</i>
<i>It's so pretty.</i>

39:58.662 --> 40:00.865
BILLY: We got rid
of that '70s carpet, Mare.

40:00.931 --> 40:02.399
-You know? You're going
to be okay with that?
-Aw.

40:02.466 --> 40:04.568
-That's not coming back?
-No, that's not coming back.

40:04.635 --> 40:06.971
<i>BILLY:</i>
<i>When Marianne reacted</i>
<i>the way she did,</i>

40:07.037 --> 40:08.939
