40:09.006 --> 40:11.108
how happy she was
with the renovation.

40:11.175 --> 40:12.877
-We made sure that this...
-Oh, my rocker!

40:12.943 --> 40:14.712
-And we had to make sure
the rocker's in there.
-Oh.

40:14.779 --> 40:17.648
And-and Rob put a-a finisher
on there just to freshen it up,

40:17.715 --> 40:20.117
-and the wood drank it in
very, very nicely.
-Oh, my God.

40:20.184 --> 40:22.086
We kept the rocking chair there

40:22.153 --> 40:24.021
because that's where she's
rocked all her grandbabies.

40:24.088 --> 40:26.757
He's told us all the wonderful
things you've done

40:26.824 --> 40:29.026
and just how you took him in
and treated him like a son.

40:29.093 --> 40:30.895
-I mean, come on.
-BILLY: She has.
-Hug Billy.

40:30.961 --> 40:33.731
-I have to hug Billy.
-I love you. I love you.

40:33.798 --> 40:34.899
<i>NISCHELLE:</i>
<i>I think it was overwhelming</i>

40:34.965 --> 40:37.168
for her, all of this
to take in in a day.

40:37.234 --> 40:40.471
That's beautiful.
She has really such good taste.

40:40.538 --> 40:41.939
But she is so happy,

40:42.006 --> 40:44.608
and that makes us
just incredibly happy.

40:44.675 --> 40:46.177
-Open the door for you.
-Thank you.

40:46.243 --> 40:47.745
-Let's go relax in your new
patio area.
-Go back outside.

40:47.812 --> 40:50.114
-Yes.
-What do you think?
-Hello! So?

40:50.181 --> 40:52.116
-Oh, this gang.
-Oh, nice.
-What did you think?

40:52.183 --> 40:53.884
Oh, it's beautiful. Great job.

40:53.951 --> 40:56.687
Upstairs is just
unbelievably...

40:56.754 --> 40:59.190
You have a whole new extension
of your house to enjoy.

40:59.256 --> 41:01.559
-I do. I need more family now.
-(laughter)

41:01.625 --> 41:02.927
NISCHELLE:
You got us now.

41:02.993 --> 41:06.197
I'll have to send out invites,
right?

41:06.263 --> 41:09.533
You really made an impact
on someone's life

41:09.600 --> 41:11.669
like you made on his life.

41:11.735 --> 41:14.038
You know,
what does that say to you?

41:14.104 --> 41:16.974
Billy came into our life
as Joe's friend,

41:17.041 --> 41:18.809
and then he became family,

41:18.876 --> 41:21.078
and then we've just been close.

41:21.145 --> 41:22.847
<i>Oh, my God.</i>

41:22.913 --> 41:24.849
<i>My husband--</i>

41:24.915 --> 41:26.217
he'd have been blown away.

41:26.283 --> 41:27.918
He'd have been shouting,
"Billy! Billy!

41:27.985 --> 41:29.220
I can't believe it. Billy."

41:29.286 --> 41:31.956
Yeah, they-they did
really like each other

41:32.022 --> 41:34.558
and had a good time together.
But he would have.

41:34.625 --> 41:36.660
He probably would have cried
like I did.

41:36.727 --> 41:39.663
After my husband died,
I went out to California

41:39.730 --> 41:41.932
and spent about nine
or ten Thanksgivings out there

41:41.999 --> 41:43.701
with Billy.
