41:43.767 --> 41:46.070
-you know?
It's just like family.
-Mm.

41:46.136 --> 41:48.205
-The most important thing
is family.
-Yeah. Yeah.

41:48.272 --> 41:49.974
I just want to express to you

41:50.040 --> 41:52.176
why you were the top choice
for this.

41:52.243 --> 41:55.246
It's because of who you are

41:55.312 --> 41:58.282
and the love that
you've shown me over the years

41:58.349 --> 42:00.851
and, uh, for giving me
my best friend.

42:00.918 --> 42:03.153
-Aw.
-So I love you. Thank you.

42:03.220 --> 42:04.622
<i>To be able to come</i>

42:04.688 --> 42:07.124
and give back was
an incredible opportunity,

42:07.191 --> 42:09.593
and I'm very grateful
for that.

42:09.660 --> 42:11.061
-I love you, Mare.
-I love you back.

42:11.128 --> 42:13.163
<i>-Salud,</i> everybody.
-Group hug. Group hug.

42:13.230 --> 42:14.765
-Group hug.
-Group hug. Then let's sit.

42:14.832 --> 42:16.233
<i>BILLY: Because she is</i>
<i>incredibly deserving</i>

42:16.300 --> 42:17.568
of something like this.

42:17.635 --> 42:18.903
NISCHELLE:
It's a perfect day.

42:18.969 --> 42:20.004
How 'bout this, Mare?

42:20.070 --> 42:21.171
-ROB: Oh, this is nice.
-Whoo-hoo!

42:21.238 --> 42:22.306
NISCHELLE:
It's a perfect day.

42:22.373 --> 42:24.742
-This is Pittsburgh weather.
-Right?

42:24.808 --> 42:25.843
<i>She was one of the people</i>
<i>in our corner</i>

42:25.910 --> 42:26.844
<i>saying, "You guys can do it."</i>

42:26.911 --> 42:28.012
<i>So to be able to bring</i>

42:28.078 --> 42:29.613
<i>this surprise renovation</i>

42:29.680 --> 42:31.749
back here for her
and gift her this

42:31.815 --> 42:33.751
is just a huge honor.

42:33.817 --> 42:35.152
-To Mare!
-To Mare. Cheers.

